# Jira space

When creating, searching, or referencing Jira work for this repository, use the **MailCraft** space (Jira project/space name).

- Prefer **MailCraft** as the project or space identifier when tools ask for a project, space, or site context tied to Mailcraft development.
- If a tool requires a project key and differs from the display name, use the key that maps to the MailCraft project in your Jira instance; the canonical human-facing name for this product area is **MailCraft**.
